sequenceDiagram
    participant Run as "run_daily.py"
    participant Spider as "Spider"
    participant Pipe as "PostgresPipeline"
    participant DB as "PostgreSQL"
    participant Clean as "DataCleaner"

    Note over Run,Clean: Step 1: 爬蟲寫入 DB
    Run->>Spider: fetch_daily("2330", 2026, 4)
    Spider->>TWSE: GET STOCK_DAY API
    TWSE-->>Spider: JSON (民國年、千分位)
    Spider->>Spider: parse & 清理 (民國→西元、去逗號)
    loop 每筆資料
        Spider->>Pipe: save_items(item)
        alt 滿 500 筆
            Pipe->>DB: INSERT ... ON CONFLICT DO UPDATE
            DB-->>Pipe: OK
        end
    end
    Spider-->>Run: {success, count}

    Note over Run,Clean: Step 2: 清洗 (原地 UPDATE)
    Run->>Clean: run_all()
    Clean->>DB: UPDATE stock_daily SET master_check='OK'
    Clean->>DB: UPDATE stock_daily SET name, industry FROM stock_master
    Clean->>DB: UPDATE tpex_cb_daily SET master_check='OK'|'NOT_FOUND'
    Clean->>DB: UPDATE tpex_cb_daily SET cb_name_enriched, conversion_price_enriched FROM cb_master
    DB-->>Clean: done
    Clean-->>Run: {stock_daily: {ok, not_found}, tpex_cb_daily: {ok, not_found}}